{"data":{"page":{"html":"<h1 id=\"option-retry-numberboolean-optional-1\"><a href=\"#option-retry-numberboolean-optional-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Option \"retry\" (number|boolean, optional, 1)</h1>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<h2><a href=\"#toc\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#usage\">Usage</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>Setting the \"retry\" option provides control over how many time an action is re-scheduled on error before it is finally treated as a failure.</p>\n<p>It is commonly used conjointly with the <a href=\"/options/attempt/\">\"attempt\" option</a> which provide an indicator over how many times an action was rescheduled.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<p>The default value is \"1\" which means that actions are not rescheduled on error.</p>\n<p>If provided as an number, the value must be superior or equal to <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>. For example, the value 3 means the action will be executed at maximum 3 times. If the third time the action fail, then it will be treated by the Nikita session as a failed action.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'nikita'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> attempt<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  count<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">assert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Set the value as <code class=\"language-text\">true</code> for an unlimited number of retries. The value <code class=\"language-text\">false</code> is the same as <code class=\"language-text\">1</code>.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/options/retry/","edit_url":"https://github.com/adaltas/node-nikita-docs/edit/master/src/md/options/retry.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Option \"retry\"","description":null,"keywords":null}}},"pageContext":{}}